name: Sea Island Preserve
address: 1027 Island Preserve Road, Johns Island, South Carolina 29455
description:
ABOUT THE HOME ENERGY RATING SCALE
The HERS (Home Energy Rating System) Index allows buyers to compare the relative energy efficiency of different homes. The HERS Index home energy rating is determined by an independent RESNET-certified home energy rater ("Rater"). The lower a home’s score, the more energy efficient it is in comparison to the HERS referenced home. For every one-point decrease in the HERS Index score, there is a corresponding one percent (1%) reduction in energy consumption as compared to a home with a HERS Index of 100. A home with a HERS score of 100 reflects a home built to 2006 IEEC Building Codes. See the bottom of this page for more information on HERS scores.

amenities.name: Resort-style swimming
amenities.description: Resort-style swimming pool with a splash and play area for kids, on open air pavilion, playground and large deck area overlooking one of the many water features and greenways.

amenities.name: Within private
amenities.description: Within the private gates of Sea Island Preserve lies estate-sized homesites with an abundance of beautiful Live Oaks throughout property.

amenities.name: Half Sea
amenities.description: Half of Sea Island Preserve's total acreage is devoted to parks and nature.  You will be able to enjoy planned walking and biking trails and greenways will provide countless opportunities to connect with neighbors and friends.

amenities.name: Neighbors can
amenities.description: Neighbors can come together for a friendly game of pickleball on one of the two planned courts.

amenities.name: Fiber network
amenities.description: Fiber network provides up to Gigabit Internet speeds

amenities.name: All homes
amenities.description: All homes include high-speed internet service and 175 tv channels provided by Spectrum included within HOA quarterly fees.
